"  Dip:","4 ounces crumbled blue cheese","3/4 cup mayonnaise","1/4 cup sour cream","1 tablespoon red wine vinegar","1 tablespoon lemon juice","1/4 teaspoon garlic powder","  Salt and pepper","  Wings:","1/4 cup ketchup","1/4 cup hot sauce (such as Frank's RedHot)","1/3 cup red wine vinegar","1 tablespoon spicy brown mustard","1 tablespoon Worcestershire sauce","1 teaspoon onion powder","1 teaspoon garlic powder","1 tablespoon sugar","4 tablespoons unsalted butter","3 pounds chicken wings, tips removed, wings separated at joints"